  "payload_text": "<!-- start of nrao-header.html -->\n<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\">\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\">\n    <link REL=\"icon\" HREF=\"/common/favicon.ico\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/common/nraostyle.css\" media=\"screen\">\n    <!-- end of nrao-header.html -->\n\n\n<title>Service Decommissioned</title>\n\n  <!-- Start of nrao-nav1.html -->\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div id=\"main\">\n      <div id=\"topbar\">\n\t<div id=\"logo\">\n\t  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/\">\n\t    <img align=\"left\" src=\"https://www.nrao.edu/icons/nrao_logo_pms_51.png\" alt=\"NRAO\"\n\t\t border=\"0\" width=\"39\" height=\"51\">\n\t  </a>\n\t  National Radio<br>Astronomy Observatory\n\t</div>\n\t<div id=\"search\">\n\t  <form name=\"gs\" method=\"get\" action=\"https://search.nrao.edu/search\" style=\"display: inline;\">\n\t    <input type=\"text\" name=\"q\" size=\"15\" maxlength=\"255\"  />\n\t    <input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"Search NRAO\" />\n\t  </form>\n\t</div>\n\t<div id=\"subnavArea\">\n\t  <!-- End of nrao-nav1.html -->\n\n\n&nbsp;<a class=\"navig\" href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/\">NRAO Home</a> &gt;\nArchive\n\n          <!-- Start of nrao-nav2nomenu.html -->\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\t\n    <hr style=\"height:1px;\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n      <tr>\n\t<td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" id=\"contentArea\">\n      \n\n\n<h3>Legacy Archive Service Retired</h3>\n\n<p>The legacy NRAO archive at archive.nrao.edu, which has served the community for many years, has been retired.</p>\n\n<p>The new NRAO Archive Access Tool at\n  <a href=\"https://data.nrao.edu\">data.nrao.edu<a>\n      is now the primary service for all NRAO science data products, providing access to VLA (historical and post-upgrade), ALMA (Cycles 1 and higher), VLBA, and significant fraction of GBT data. More details on these may be found at the new archive tool's web site.</p>\n\n<p>For questions or help, please contact the NRAO science help desk\n  (<a href=\"https://help.nrao.edu\">https://help.nrao.edu</a>)\n  and select the \"Data Products\" topic.</p>\n\n<h3>The new archive is here: <a href=\"https://data.nrao.edu\">https://data.nrao.edu</a>.</h3>\n\n<!-- Start of nrao-trailer.html -->\n<div id=\"footerUtilities\">\n  <a href=\"https://staff.nrao.edu/\">Staff</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/cgi-bin/contact\">Contact Us</a> |\n<!--\n  <a href=\"https://careers.nrao.edu/\">Careers</a> |\n-->\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/admin/hr/careers.shtml\">Careers</a> |\n\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/navbar/directories.shtml\">Directories</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/navbar/sitemap.shtml\">Site Map</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/index.php/Help\">Help</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/policy/\">Policies</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu/policy/diversity.shtml\">Diversity</a> |\n  <a href=\"http://search.nrao.edu/\">Search</a>\n</div>\n<div id=\"footer\">\n <a href=\"http://www.nrao.edu\">\n  <img src=\"/common/logoNRAO.jpg\" alt=\"NRAO\"\n   width=\"41\" height=\"41\" vspace=\"5\" border=\"0\" align=\"middle\"\n   style=\"float:left;\" />\n </a>\n <a href=\"http://www.nsf.gov/\">\n  <img src=\"/common/logoNSF.jpg\" alt=\"NSF\"\n   width=\"57\" height=\"57\" hspace=\"10\" border=\"0\" align=\"middle\"\n   style=\"float:left;\" />\n </a> \n <a href=\"http://www.aui.edu/\">\n  <img src=\"/common/logoAUI.gif\" alt=\"AUI\"\n   width=\"74\" height=\"49\" vspace=\"1\" border=\"0\" align=\"middle\"\n   style=\"float:left; margin-right:20px;\" />\n </a> \n <p style=\"padding-top:10px;\">\n  Copyright &#169; 2009 Associated Universities, Inc.<br>\n  The National Radio Astronomy Observatory is a facility of the National\n  Science Foundation operated under cooperative agreement by Associated\n  Universities, Inc.\n </p>  \n</div>\n<!-- End of nrao-trailer.html -->\n\n\n<em>Modified on \nMonday, 18-Apr-2022 13:56:12 MDT\n</em>\n\n<!-- Start of nrao-end.html -->\n\n\n\t\t</td>\n\t</tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\n<!-- End of nrao-end.html -->\n"
